{"word":"παραδοξολογέω","slug":"παραδοξολογέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραδοξολογέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:παραδοξολόγος'><el>παραδοξολόγος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to tell marvels</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>πολλὰ παραδοξολογεῖται</el> many <i>marvels are told</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/>"}]}